---
/*
  VOICE REFERENCES:
  
  PROPHET: "The hour is late. YAHUAH calls His remnant. Will you answer?"
  OG MENTOR: "I'll tell you what nobody else will: repentance isn't optional."
  HOOD PHILOSOPHER: "They sold you religion. YAHUSHA offers relationship. Know the difference."
  ENTREPRENEUR: "Seven days. One reset. The return? Everything."
  
  SACRED NAMES: YAHUAH, YAHUSHA, RUACH HAQODESH, EL ELYON
*/
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Start Here">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-amber-100">Start Here</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h2>What We Believe</h2>
      <p>
        YAHUAH is the Most High. YAHUSHA is Mashiach—fully God, fully man, crucified and resurrected. 
        The RUACH HAQODESH empowers believers to walk in holiness. Scripture is our final authority. 
        Repentance is not optional. The remnant will be refined.
      </p>

      <h2>The Path Forward</h2>
      <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6 my-6 not-prose">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-amber-100 font-bold text-lg mb-1">Learn</div>
            <div class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Truth from Scripture</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-amber-700 text-2xl hidden md:block">→</div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-amber-100 font-bold text-lg mb-1">Apply</div>
            <div class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Walk it out daily</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-amber-700 text-2xl hidden md:block">→</div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-amber-100 font-bold text-lg mb-1">Share</div>
            <div class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Declare the Gospel</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-amber-700 text-2xl hidden md:block">→</div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-amber-100 font-bold text-lg mb-1">Gather</div>
            <div class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Build the remnant</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>7-Day Reset</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">
        A week to strip the noise, hear YAHUAH clearly, and reset your spiritual foundation.
      </p>
      
      <div class="space-y-4 not-prose">
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border-l-4 border-amber-700 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold text-amber-100 mb-1">Day 1: Repentance</div>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Confess. Turn from sin. Plead the blood of YAHUSHA.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border-l-4 border-amber-700 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold text-amber-100 mb-1">Day 2: The Word</div>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Read Scripture—no commentary. Let YAHUAH speak.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border-l-4 border-amber-700 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold text-amber-100 mb-1">Day 3: Prayer & Fasting</div>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Deny the flesh. Sharpen your spiritual senses.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border-l-4 border-amber-700 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold text-amber-100 mb-1">Day 4: Worship</div>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Praise YAHUAH. Exalt His Name. No distractions.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border-l-4 border-amber-700 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold text-amber-100 mb-1">Day 5: Spiritual Warfare</div>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Put on the armor. Close doorways. Stand firm.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border-l-4 border-amber-700 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold text-amber-100 mb-1">Day 6: Identity</div>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Who are you in YAHUSHA? Walk in it.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border-l-4 border-amber-700 p-4">
          <div class="font-bold text-amber-100 mb-1">Day 7: Commission</div>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Go. Share the Gospel. Train others.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="/spiritual-warfare" class="inline-block bg-amber-700 hover:bg-amber-600 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black transition-colors not-prose">
          Continue to Spiritual Warfare
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
